The Insurance cover shall be up to;
 i) Rs. 2.5 lakhs per annum for a family of three or less members and up to; 
ii) Rs. 4 Lakhs for a family of four and more members.
The Insurance benefits can be availed individually or collectively by members of the family. Pre-existing medical conditions are to be covered from day one, subject to the exclusions given in Annexure 5B
